  "text": "The influence of WF on the glutathione-S-transferase activity (A, nmol rypsin-like enzyme activity, the major catalytic activity of the 20S β proteasome catalytic subunit, [CITATION_1] , in myotubes after treatment with WF. Protein degradation was enhanced in C 2 C 12 myotubes treated with WF, in parallel to an intense depression of protein synthesis, as observed in skeletal muscle of cachectic cancer patients.",
